1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>OpenGL 구동 환경</h4>\n<p>OpenGL 강의에 사용되는 개발 환경은 Windows 10, Visual Studio 2017 이며, 사용되는 언어는 C 언어입니다.<br />\n또한, OpenGL 버전은 현재 4.6 버전까지 나와있지만, 기본부터 설명해야 하기 때문에 1.0부터 시작하도록 하겠습니다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"1-glut-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-glut-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"1 glut 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. GLUT 설치</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.opengl.org/resources/libraries/glut/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.opengl.org/resources/libraries/glut/</a> 에 들어가서 Pre-complied Win32 for Intel GLUT 3.7 DLLs for Windows 95 &#x26; NT를 다운로드 받는다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 900px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8585c65ea77361b90a529f8ee4f93259/1cfc2/opengl_1_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 98.1111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Image\"\n        title=\"Image\"\n        src=\"/static/8585c65ea77361b90a529f8ee4f93259/1cfc2/opengl_1_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8585c65ea77361b90a529f8ee4f93259/8ff5a/opengl_1_1.png 240w,\n/static/8585c65ea77361b90a529f8ee4f93259/e85cb/opengl_1_1.png 480w,\n/static/8585c65ea77361b90a529f8ee4f93259/1cfc2/opengl_1_1.png 900w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4 id=\"2-glut-라이브러리-압축해제\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-glut-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC-%EC%95%95%EC%B6%95%ED%95%B4%EC%A0%9C\" aria-label=\"2 glut 라이브러리 압축해제 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. GLUT 라이브러리 압축해제</h4>\n<p>glutdlls37beta.zip (18.12.17 기준) 파일이 받아지면, 압축을 해제합니다.<br />\n폴더 내에는 glut.dll, glut32.dll, glut.h, glut.lib, glut32.lib 파일 목록이 보입니다.<br />\n해당 파일들을 프로젝트에서 로드하기 위해서는 각각의 경로로 파일을 이동해야 합니다.<br /></p>\n<h4 id=\"3-glut-라이브러리-경로설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-glut-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC-%EA%B2%BD%EB%A1%9C%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"3 glut 라이브러리 경로설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. GLUT 라이브러리 경로설정</h4>\n<p>윈도우 절대 경로로 설정 ( 한 번 지정해두면 Visual Studio 에서는 다음에 설정할 필요가 없음 )</p>\n<p>  a. 절대 경로 확인 방법</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"> (1) glut.h\n    - &#39;C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Windows Kits\\10\\Include\\&lt;마지막버전&gt;\\um\\gl&#39; 폴더 내에 저장합니다.\n    </code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 700px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/44dae30b31db10818f1dad1e55846c2c/8c557/opengl_1_2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.71428571428571%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Image\"\n        title=\"Image\"\n        src=\"/static/44dae30b31db10818f1dad1e55846c2c/8c557/opengl_1_2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/44dae30b31db10818f1dad1e55846c2c/8ff5a/opengl_1_2.png 240w,\n/static/44dae30b31db10818f1dad1e55846c2c/e85cb/opengl_1_2.png 480w,\n/static/44dae30b31db10818f1dad1e55846c2c/8c557/opengl_1_2.png 700w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"> (2) glut.lib, glut32.lib\n     - &#39;C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Windows Kits\\10\\Lib\\10.0.16299.0\\um\\&lt;빌드할 버전&gt;&#39; 폴더 내에 저장합니다.\n     </code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 700px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8f25ea11eaa3b377cace7bc9ce6a09f7/29d31/opengl_1_3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.714285714285715%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Image\"\n        title=\"Image\"\n        src=\"/static/8f25ea11eaa3b377cace7bc9ce6a09f7/29d31/opengl_1_3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8f25ea11eaa3b377cace7bc9ce6a09f7/09b79/opengl_1_3.jpg 240w,\n/static/8f25ea11eaa3b377cace7bc9ce6a09f7/7cc5e/opengl_1_3.jpg 480w,\n/static/8f25ea11eaa3b377cace7bc9ce6a09f7/29d31/opengl_1_3.jpg 700w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"> (3) glut.dll, glut32.dll\n     - Windows 10 64bit 인 경우 : &#39;C:\\Windows\\SysWOW64&#39; 폴더 내에 저장\n     - Windows 10 32bit 인 경우 : &#39;C:\\Windows\\System32&#39; 폴더 내에 저장\n     </code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 700px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0c4750f18d905dd618fadc26ce648ffc/8c557/opengl_1_4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-imag